This allow you to preview any cloze, not just number 1, as in this image.
<img src="https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-any-cloze-in-preview/raw/master/ex.png"/>

To report a bug, and for more information, please go to https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-any-cloze-in-preview

